  63. (* Invert a test *)

  65. ‌let invert_integer_test = function
  66.     Isigned cmp -> Isigned(Cmm.negate_integer_comparison cmp)
  67.   | Iunsigned cmp -> Iunsigned(Cmm.negate_integer_comparison cmp)

  69. ‌let invert_test = function
  70.     Itruetest -> Ifalsetest
  71.   | Ifalsetest -> Itruetest
  72.   | Iinttest(cmp) -> Iinttest(invert_integer_test cmp)
  73.   | Iinttest_imm(cmp, n) -> Iinttest_imm(invert_integer_test cmp, n)
  74.   | Ifloattest(cmp) -> Ifloattest(Cmm.negate_float_comparison cmp)
  75.   | Ieventest -> Ioddtest
  76.   | Ioddtest -> Ieventest

  78. (* The "end" instruction *)

  80. ‌let rec end_instr =
  81.   { desc = Lend;
  82.     next = end_instr;
  83.     arg = [||];
  84.     res = [||];
  85.     dbg = Debuginfo.none;
  86.     live = Reg.Set.empty }

  88. (* Cons an instruction (live, debug empty) *)

  90. let instr_cons d a r n =
  91.   { desc = d; next = n; arg = a; res = r;
  92.     dbg = Debuginfo.none; live = Reg.Set.empty }
